# 1x FS0883. One focused interlude estimated to Zod assembly.
# 2026-07-04 (2): burn 28 -> 16. Cleared: 8x FS0033 via the OPAQUE/ERASED PREFIX COLLAPSE
# (generic applications onto handle/Erased/obj heads carry policy-meaningless args —
# `Zod.ZodType<...>` deep trees and `obj<...>` scrub residue collapse to the bare head;
