# `ServiceWorkerGlobalScope.URL` refs vs where the nested def actually emitted);
# FS0033 x70 (arity classes, grew +20 as deeper typechecking unmasked sites);
# FS0035 x22 + FS0953 x4: ALIAS-BODY LEAF-DROP — alias bodies referencing nested
# children print the PARENT name bare (leaf lost, NOT scrubbed: `type
# LoopbackForExport<'T> = option<U3<LoopbackForExport, ...>>` self-cycles), an
