#  - BARE-GENERIC DEFAULT SYNTHESIS extended to the `ResolvedType = Some` lazy side
#    (previously fell to the render-inner-alone arm, emitting bare `WritableStream`
#    against `type WritableStream<'W>`), and CONSTRUCTOR RETURNS self-apply the type's
#    own typars (`abstract Create: ... -> WritableStream<'W>`, was bare).
#  - MEMOIZED PER-EXPORT SCOPE STORES (ctx.ExportScopeStores): nested children register
#    only on FRESH mints, so the scrub-armed second export pass with fresh stores
